cu.explanation_en: Setting Asn1_verbosity to an unknown enum 'invalid' will cause ASN.1 verbosity configuration failure and prevent proper ASN.1 message handling.

du.explanation_en: Setting Asn1_verbosity to an unknown enum 'invalid' will cause ASN.1 verbosity configuration failure and prevent proper ASN.1 message handling.
du.explanation_zh: 將 Asn1_verbosity 設定為未知的枚舉值 'invalid'，會導致 ASN.1 詳細程度配置失敗，並阻止正確的 ASN.1 訊息處理。
